### Phase F: Smoke + Phase-2-Doc + PR (1h)
- [ ] Manual smoke walkthrough as per DK-16. Update `memory/lessons.md` with anything surprising encountered.
- [ ] Create `tasks/m2-phase2-checklist.md` with the operator checklist (DNS, Mailu, ENV, smoke, rollback).
